{
  "name": "3 Ioan",
  "chapters": [
    {
      "name": "3 Ioan 1",
      "chapter": 1,
      "link": "https://biblia.resursecrestine.ro/3-ioan",
      "verses": [
        {
          "type": "title",
          "text": "A TREIA EPISTOL\u0102 A LUI IOAN"
        },
        {
          "name": "3 Ioan 1:1",
          "type": "verse",
          "number": 1,
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": "Prezbiterul"
            },
            {
              "type": "note",
              "text": "1"
            },
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": " c\u0103tre preaiubitul Gaius, pe"
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "text": "*"
            },
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": " care-l iubesc \u00een adev\u0103r."
            }
          ],
          "references": {
            "*": [
              "2 Ioan 1:1"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "3 Ioan 1:2",
          "type": "verse",
          "number": 2,
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": "Preaiubitule, doresc ca toate lucrurile tale s\u0103-\u0163i mearg\u0103 bine \u015fi s\u0103n\u0103tatea ta s\u0103 sporeasc\u0103 tot a\u015fa cum spore\u015fte sufletul t\u0103u."
            }
          ],
          "references": {}
        },
        {
          "name": "3 Ioan 1:3",
          "type": "verse",
          "number": 3,
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": "A fost o mare bucurie pentru mine c\u00e2nd au venit fra\u0163ii \u015fi au m\u0103rturisit c\u0103 e\u015fti credincios adev\u0103rului \u015fi c\u0103 umbli"
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "text": "*"
            },
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": " \u00een adev\u0103r."
            }
          ],
          "references": {
            "*": [
              "2 Ioan 1:4"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "3 Ioan 1:4",
          "type": "verse",
          "number": 4,
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": "Eu n-am bucurie mai mare dec\u00e2t s\u0103 aud despre copiii"
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "text": "*"
            },
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": " mei c\u0103 umbl\u0103 \u00een adev\u0103r."
            }
          ],
          "references": {
            "*": [
              "1 Cor 4:15",
              "Filim 1:10"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "3 Ioan 1:5",
          "type": "verse",
          "number": 5,
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": "Preaiubitule, tu lucrezi cu credincio\u015fie \u00een tot ce faci pentru fra\u0163i \u015fi pentru str\u0103ini totodat\u0103."
            }
          ],
          "references": {}
        },
        {
          "name": "3 Ioan 1:6",
          "type": "verse",
          "number": 6,
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": "Ei au m\u0103rturisit despre dragostea ta \u00eenaintea Bisericii. Vei face bine s\u0103 \u00eengrije\u015fti de c\u0103l\u0103toria lor \u00eentr-un chip vrednic de Dumnezeu,"
            }
          ],
          "references": {}
        },
        {
          "name": "3 Ioan 1:7",
          "type": "verse",
          "number": 7,
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": "c\u0103ci au plecat pentru dragostea Numelui Lui, f\u0103r\u0103 s\u0103 primeasc\u0103 ceva"
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "text": "*"
            },
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": " de la neamuri."
            }
          ],
          "references": {
            "*": [
              "1 Cor 9:12",
              "1 Cor 9:15"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "3 Ioan 1:8",
          "type": "verse",
          "number": 8,
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": "Este datoria noastr\u0103 dar s\u0103 primim bine pe astfel de oameni, ca s\u0103 lucr\u0103m \u00eempreun\u0103 cu adev\u0103rul."
            }
          ],
          "references": {}
        },
        {
          "name": "3 Ioan 1:9",
          "type": "verse",
          "number": 9,
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": "Am scris ceva Bisericii, dar Diotref, c\u0103ruia \u00eei place s\u0103 aib\u0103 \u00eent\u00e2ietatea \u00eentre ei, nu vrea s\u0103 \u015ftie de noi."
            }
          ],
          "references": {}
        },
        {
          "name": "3 Ioan 1:10",
          "type": "verse",
          "number": 10,
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": "De aceea, c\u00e2nd voi veni, \u00eei voi aduce aminte de faptele pe care le face, c\u0103ci ne clevete\u015fte cu vorbe rele. Nu se mul\u0163ume\u015fte cu at\u00e2t, dar nici el nu prime\u015fte pe fra\u0163i \u015fi \u00eempiedic\u0103 \u015fi pe cei ce voiesc s\u0103-i primeasc\u0103 \u015fi-i d\u0103 afar\u0103 din Biseric\u0103."
            }
          ],
          "references": {}
        },
        {
          "name": "3 Ioan 1:11",
          "type": "verse",
          "number": 11,
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": "Preaiubitule, nu"
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "text": "*"
            },
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": " urma r\u0103ul, ci binele. Cine"
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "text": "**"
            },
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": " face binele este din Dumnezeu; cine face r\u0103ul n-a v\u0103zut pe Dumnezeu."
            }
          ],
          "references": {
            "*": [
              "Ps 37:27",
              "Isa 1:16",
              "Isa 1:17",
              "1 Pet 3:11"
            ],
            "**": [
              "1 Ioan 2:29",
              "1 Ioan 3:6",
              "1 Ioan 3:9"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "3 Ioan 1:12",
          "type": "verse",
          "number": 12,
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": "To\u0163i, chiar \u015fi Adev\u0103rul, m\u0103rturisesc bine despre"
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "text": "*"
            },
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": " Dimitrie; \u015fi noi m\u0103rturisim despre el: \u015fi"
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "text": "**"
            },
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": " \u015ftii c\u0103 m\u0103rturisirea noastr\u0103 este adev\u0103rat\u0103."
            }
          ],
          "references": {
            "*": [
              "1 Tim 3:7"
            ],
            "**": [
              "Ioan 21:24"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "3 Ioan 1:13",
          "type": "verse",
          "number": 13,
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": "A\u015f avea s\u0103-\u0163i spun multe"
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "text": "*"
            },
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": " lucruri, dar nu voiesc s\u0103 \u0163i le scriu cu cerneal\u0103 \u015fi condei."
            }
          ],
          "references": {
            "*": [
              "2 Ioan 1:12"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "3 Ioan 1:14",
          "type": "verse",
          "number": 14,
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": "N\u0103d\u0103jduiesc s\u0103 te v\u0103d \u00een cur\u00e2nd \u015fi atunci vom vorbi gur\u0103 c\u0103tre gur\u0103. Pacea s\u0103 fie cu tine.Prietenii \u00ee\u0163i trimit s\u0103n\u0103tate. Spune s\u0103n\u0103tate prietenilor, fiec\u0103ruia pe nume. Amin."
            }
          ],
          "references": {}
        }
      ],
      "notes": {
        "1)": " Sau: b\u0103tr\u00e2nul."
      }
    }
  ]
}